headline.main: Dayton to Spend 1 More Day at Mayo After Prostate Surgery
headline.print_headline: Dayton to Spend 1 More Day at Mayo After Prostate Surgery

lead_paragraph: Minnesota Gov. Mark Dayton will spend one more day at the Mayo Clinic in Rochester after undergoing surgery for prostate cancer.
